            <trans-unit id="VGhlIHVwbG9hZGVkIGZpbGUgZXhjZWVkcyB0aGUgbWF4aW11bSBzaXplIHNldCBpbiB0aGUgSFRNTCBmb3JtIHZpYSB0aGUgTUFYX0ZJTEVfU0laRSB2YWx1ZS4=">
                <source>The uploaded file exceeds the maximum size set in the HTML form via the MAX_FILE_SIZE value.</source>
                <target>Il file caricato supera la dimensione massima indicata nel modulo HTML con l’istruzione MAX_FILE_SIZE.</target>
